I noticed a few issues in the LoginActivity class that could cause errors or crashes. Here are the necessary fixes:

```java:app/src/main/java/com/finedine/rms/LoginActivity.java
// ... existing code ...

// Remove duplicate import
import java.security.spec.KeySpec;

// ... existing code ...

private void saveUserSession(int userId, String role, String name) {
 SharedPreferences sharedPreferences = getSharedPreferences("UserSession", MODE_PRIVATE);
 SharedPreferences.Editor editor = sharedPreferences.edit();
 editor.putInt("userId", userId);
 editor.putString("role", role);
 editor.putString("name", name);
